OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSainsbury's to recruit     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F18,000 Christmas workers   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sainsbury's has announced it is looking
OL,6, to recruit 18,000 temporary workers to 
OL,7, support the supermarket through the    
OL,8, festive season.                        
OL,10,FThe company said it was hiring workers 
OL,11,Ffor 15,000 roles at Sainsbury's, 2,000 
OL,12,Fat Argos and 1,000 in its logistics    
OL,13,Fdivision which runs its warehouses.    
OL,15,FSainsbury's said new recruits would be 
OL,16,Fpaid #10.25 an hour, with London-based 
OL,17,Fstaff getting #11.30.                  
OL,19,FSeasonal workers will also receive free
OL,20,Ffood during shifts and a discount card.
